Img2epub Converter

Description

    Convert images into epub documents. ".epub" is the file extension of an XML format for reflowable digital books and publications.

Portability

    Linux, Windows and potentially all OS where dependcies are ported to.

Input format

    Supported file formats : .cbz, .cbr, directory

Output format

    Supported file formats : .epub (http://www.idpf.org/)

Fonctionnality

    * Resize
    * Trim borders
    * Reduce Color
    * Cut in two pieces all, horizontal or vertical images
    * ...

Dependencies

    * ImageMagick
    * 7-Zip
    * Cygwin (for MS Windows users) with following packages :
          o uuidgen (e2fsprogs : Ext2 filesystem utilities)
          o bash and common command line tools (sed, gawk, ...)


see http://code.google.com/p/img2epub/ for more informations and last version
